g crowds.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Some of the highlights of this episode include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>getting asked to speak at SXSW which led to a book deal</li>\n<li>how publishing a book impacted Lisa’s business</li>\n<li>how attending several WordCamps was the catalyst for her partnership with WebDev</li>\n<li>and just what is a designoveloper?</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Watch the entire interview below and check out the <a href="http://www.wpelevation.com/2014/07/episode-43-lisa-sabin-wilson-webdev-studios/">blog post by WP Elevation</a>.</p>\n<p><iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/101681657" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" title="WP Elevation - Lisa Sabin-Wilson" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:87:"http://webdevstudios.com/2014/08/04/lisa-sabin-wilson-interview-with-wp-elevation/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:63:"\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n    \n        \n      \n    \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"Don’t repeat yourself! How to create an Author Box using the Gravatar API";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:87:"http://webdevstudios.com/2014/07/31/how-to-create-an-author-box-using-the-gravatar-api/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17